        <abstract>
            <p>Has enjoyed CD’s last publications, especially on self-fertilisation of plants.</p>
            <p>Believes a visit by CD to the U. S. would do much to promote his theories.</p>
            <p>Reports on American campaign against locusts [by C. V. Riley].</p>
        </abstract>
